 "html": "\n<div class=\"contenedor\">\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"  >\n     <tr>\n        <td  width=\"40%\">\n           <img src=\"/files/logoMovilidad.png\">            \n        </td> \n        <td width=\"60%\">\n           \n        </td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n            <div style = \"text-align: center; font-size:100%\" ><H4><strong>FORMATO \u00daNICO DE VERIFICACI\u00d3N VEHICULAR</strong></H4></div>\n<table border=\"1\"  >\n    <tr>\n        <td width=\"5%\" style=\"padding: 0px!important;border-style: none;border-top-style: hidden;border-right-style: hidden;border-left-style: hidden;border-bottom-style: hidden;\">\n            <div>FECHA: </div>\n        </td>\n        <td width=\"30%\" style=\"text-align:center;padding: 0px!important;padding: 0px!important;border-style: none;border-top-style: hidden;border-right-style: hidden;border-left-style: hidden;\">\n            <span> {{frappe.format_date(doc.fecha).upper()}}</span>\n        </td>        \n      \n        <td style=\"text-align:right;padding: 0px!important;border-style: none;border-top-style: hidden;border-right-style: hidden;border-left-style: hidden;border-bottom-style: hidden;\">\n            <div >FOLIO No.</div>\n        </td>\n        <td width=\"30%\"  style=\"text-align:center;padding: 0px!important;padding: 0px!important;border-style: none;border-top-style: hidden;border-right-style: hidden;border-left-style: hidden;\">\n            <span style=\"color:black\">{{doc.folio}}</span>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\n    <div style=\"text-align: justify ; font-size:11px\">\n        EL QUE SUSCRIBE ENCARGADO DE VERIFICACI\u00d3N VEHICULAR DE LA SECRETAR\u00cdA \n        DE MOVILIDAD DE NAYARIT EN EL MUNICIPIO DE <u>{{frappe.db.get_value('Tramite', frappe.Municipio.municipio_asignado,'municipio')}}</u> ESTADO DE NAYARIT, CERTIFICA\n        Y HACE CONSTAR QUE LOS DATOS QUE A CONTINUACI\u00d3N SE MENCIONAN SOBRE LA\n        VERIFICACI\u00d3N VEHICULAR DE LA UNIDAD QUE ME FUE PRESENTADA.  \n        <u> <strong>{{frappe.db.get_value('User', frappe.session.user, 'full_name').upper()}}</strong> </u> TEL\u00c9FONO <u> 311 1231010</u> RE\u00daNE LOS REQUISITOS\n        PARA SERVICIO P\u00daBLICO Y SU CLASIFICACI\u00d3N QUE ESTABLECE LA LEY DE MOVILIDAD EN LOS ART\u00cdCULOS\n        199 Y 205 FRACCIONES I Y II DE DICHA LEY.\n    </div>\n\n     <table border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0'>\n        <tbody>\n            <tr>\n                <td style=\"border-style: none;border-top-style: hidden;border-right-style: hidden;border-left-style: hidden; \">\n                    <div style=\"color:#8f1448;\">\n                        <strong>CLASIFICACI\u00d3N DE TRANSPORTE:</strong> \n                        <span>{{doc.clasificacion.upper()}}</span></div>\n                    \n                </td>\n            </tr>\n                           \n        </tbody>\n    </table>\n    \n    <div style=\"text-align: center ; font-size:70%\">\n     <strong><h5>PARA TAL EFECTO PRESENTO LA DOCUMENTACI\u00d3N QUE A CONTINUACI\u00d3N SE DESCRIBE</h5></strong>\n    </div>\n    \n    <table width='100%' border='0'>\n        <tbody>\n            <tr>\n                <td width=\"70%\" style=\"padding: 0px!important;\">\n                   <div style = \"text-align: center;color:black;\">DATOS DE LA FACTURA</div>\n                     <table border=\"1\" width=\"100%\">\n                        <tbody>\n                             <tr>\n                                <td >No. DE FACTURA: <span>{{doc.clave_documento}}</span></td>\n                                <td >FECHA: <span>{{frappe.format_date(doc.fecha_documento).upper()}}</span></td>\n                             </tr>\n                             <tr>\n                                <td colspan=\"2\">EXPEDIDA POR: <span> SECRETAR\u00cdA DE MOVILIDAD</span></td>\n                               \n                             </tr>                             \n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                    <div style = \"text-align: center;color:black;\"> DATOS DEL \u00daLTIMO PAGO PRESENTADO</div>\n                     <table border=\"1\" width=\"100%\">\n                        <tbody>\n                             <tr>\n                                <td>FECHA: <span>{{frappe.format_date(doc.fecha_pago).upper()}}</span></td>\n                                <td>No. DE RECIBO DE PAGO: <span>{{doc.num_ult_recibo}}</span></td>\n                             </tr>\n                             <tr>\n                           \n                                                {% if doc.nombre_municipio %}\n                                                 <td colspan=\"2\">PRESTA SERVICIO EN: <span>{{doc.nombre_municipio}}</span></td>\n                                                {% else %}\n                                                  <td colspan=\"2\">PRESTA SERVICIO EN: </td>\n                                                {% endif %}                               \n                               \n                             </tr>                             \n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>                    \n                    \n                </td>\n                <td width=\"30%\" style=\"text-align:right\">\n          \n                     <table border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0'>\n                        <tbody>\n                             <tr>\n                                <td style=\"text-align: center;padding:20px!important;\">SELLOS DEL TR\u00c1MITE<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></td>\n                             </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>                       \n                </td>                \n            </tr>\n        </tbody>\n    </table>\n                     <div style = \"text-align: center;color:black;font-size:11px; \"><strong>DATOS P\u00d3LIZA DE SEGUROS</strong></div>\n                     <table border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0'>\n                        <tbody>\n                             <tr>\n                                <td>No. P\u00d3LIZA: <span>{{doc.poliza}}</span></td>\n                                <td>VIGENCIA: <span> {{frappe.format_date(doc.fecha_vigencia_inicial).upper()}} - {{frappe.format_date(doc.fecha_vigencia_final).upper()}}</span></td>\n                             </tr>\n                             <tr>\n                               <td colspan=\"2\">NOMBRE DE ASEGURADORA: <span>{{doc.aseguradora}}</span></td>\n                             </tr>                             \n                        </tbody>\n                    </table> \n                    \n                    <div style = \"text-align: center;color:black;font-size:11px; \"><strong> DATOS DEL VEH\u00cdCULO</strong></div>\n                     <table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"padding: 0px!important;\">\n                        <tbody>\n                             <tr style=\"padding: 0px!important;\" >\n                                <td style=\"padding: 0px!important;\">\n                                    <table  border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0'>\n                                        <tbody>\n                                            <tr>\n                                                {% if doc.ruta %}\n                                                 <td>RUTA: <span>{{doc.ruta}}</span></td>\n                                                {% else %}\n                                                  <td>RUTA: </td>\n                                                {% endif %}\n                                                {% if doc.sitio %}\n                                                 <td>SITIO: <span>{{doc.sitio}}</span></td>\n                                                {% else %}\n                                                  <td>SITIO: </td>\n                                                {% endif %}                                                \n                                            </tr>\n                                        </tbody>\n                                    </table>      \n                                </td>\n                             </tr>\n                             <tr style=\"padding: 0px!important;\">\n                                <td style=\"padding: 0px!important;\">\n                                   <table border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0' style=\"border-top-style: hidden;\">\n                                    <tbody>\n                                        <tr>\n                                            {% if doc.numero_economico %}\n                                            <td width=\"35%\">No ECON\u00d3MICO: <span>{{doc.numero_economico}}</span></td>\n                                            {% else %}\n                                            <td width=\"35%\">No ECON\u00d3MICO:</td>\n                                            {% endif %}\n                                            <td width=\"30%\">PLACAS: <span>{{doc.placa}}</span></td>\n                                            <td width=\"35%\">COLOR: <span>{{doc.color_principal}}</span></td>\n                                        </tr>\n                                     </tbody>\n                                    </table> \n                                </td>\n                             </tr>  \n                             <tr style=\"padding: 0px!important;\">\n                                <td style=\"padding: 0px!important;\">\n                                   <table border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0' style=\"border-top-style: hidden;\">\n                                    <tbody>\n                                        <tr>\n                                            <td width=\"25%\">MARCA: <span>{{doc.marca.upper()}}</span></td>\n                                            <td width=\"25%\">SUB MARCA: <span>{{doc.version.upper()}}</span></td>\n                                            <td width=\"25%\">MODELO: <span>{{doc.modelo.upper()}}</span></td>\n                                            <td width=\"25%\">CAPACIDAD: <span>{{doc.numero_pasajeros}} {{doc.unidad_carga}}</span></td>\n                                        </tr>\n                                     </tbody>\n                                    </table> \n                                </td>\n                             </tr>  \n                             <tr style=\"padding: 0px!important;\">\n                                <td style=\"padding: 0px!important;\">\n                                   <table border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" style=\"border-top-style: hidden;\">\n                                    <tbody>\n                                        <tr>\n                                            <td width=\"50%\">No. SERIE: <span>{{doc.serie}}</span></td>\n                                            <td width=\"50%\">No. DE MOTOR: <span>{{doc.numero_motor}}</span></td>\n                                        </tr>\n                                     </tbody>\n                                    </table> \n                                </td>\n                             </tr>        \n                             <tr style=\"padding: 0px!important;\">\n                                <td style=\"padding: 0px!important;\">\n                                   <table border=\"1\" width=\"100%\"  style=\"border-top-style: hidden;border-top-left-radius: 3px;\">\n                                    <tbody>\n                                        <tr>\n                                                {% if doc.factura_cambio_motor %}\n                                                 <td width=\"60%\">No. DE FACTURA DE CAMBIO DE MOTOR: <span>{{doc.factura_cambio_motor}}</span></td>\n                                                {% else %}\n                                                 <td width=\"60%\">No. DE FACTURA DE CAMBIO DE MOTOR: </td>\n                                                {% endif %}\n                                            <td width=\"40%\">FOLIO REPUVE: <span>{{doc.folio_repuve}}</span></td>\n                                        </tr>\n                                     </tbody>\n                                    </table> \n                                </td>\n                             </tr>  \n                             <tr style=\"padding: 0px!important;\">\n                                <td style=\"padding: 0px!important;\">\n                                   <table border=\"1\" width=\"100%\"  style=\"border-top-style: hidden;\">\n                                    <tbody>\n                                        <tr>\n                                            <td width=\"50%\" >TR\u00c1MITE:<span> {{doc.tramite.upper()}}</span></td>\n                                            <td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-style: none;border-top-style: hidden;border-right-style: hidden;border-bottom-style:hidden; \"></td>\n                                        </tr>\n                                     </tbody>\n                                    </table> \n                                </td>\n                             </tr>                              \n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>                       \n\n<br>\n<div class=\"contenedorFooter\">\n  <img src=\"/files/logoInferiorMovilidad11.png\"> \n  <div class=\"centrado\"><small>Avenida Rey Nayar S/N. Esquina con Insurgentes, colonia Bur\u00f3cratas Federal, Tepic, Nayarit. Tel. (311) 2135712</small></div>\n</div>\n</div> <!-- div contenedor -->   \n<div class=\"noprint\">\n    <hr class=\"separador\">\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"contenedor\">\n    <table border=\"1\">\n     <tr>\n        <td  width=\"40%\" style=\"text-align:right;padding: 0px!important;border-style: none;border-top-style: hidden;border-right-style: hidden;border-left-style: hidden;border-bottom-style: hidden;\">\n           <img src=\"/files/logoMovilidad.png\">            \n        </td> \n        <td style=\"text-align:right;padding: 0px!important;border-style: none;border-top-style: hidden;border-right-style: hidden;border-left-style: hidden;border-bottom-style: hidden;\">\n            <div ><br><br><br><br><br>FOLIO No.</div>\n        </td>\n        <td width=\"30%\"  style=\"text-align:center;padding: 0px!important;padding: 0px!important;border-style: none;border-top-style: hidden;border-right-style: hidden;border-left-style: hidden;\">\n            <br><br><br><br><br><span style=\"color:black\">{{doc.folio}}</span>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\n\n\n<div style = \"text-align: center; font-size:100%\" ><H4><strong>FORMATO \u00daNICO DE VERIFICACI\u00d3N VEHICULAR</strong></H4></div>\n        \n\n\n\n    <div style=\"text-align: center ; font-size:70%\">\n     <strong><h5>MANUAL QUE DEBE CUMPLIR LAS UNIDADES TANTO EN EQUIPO DE EMERGENCIA COMO REQUISITOS\n MEC\u00c1NICOS Y DE CARROCERIA DE LO VEH\u00cdCULOS</h5></strong>\n    </div>\n<br>\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width:100%;\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr style=\"padding: 0px!important;\">\n            <td width=\"50%\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n               CONCEPTO\n            </td>\n            <td style=\"text-align:center\">\n                BUENO\n            </td>\n            <td style=\"text-align:center\">\n                MALO\n            </td>\n            <td style=\"text-align:center\">\n                OBSERVACIONES\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n  </thead>\n  {% set ns = namespace(sr = 0)%}\n  {% set requi = frappe.get_all('Requisitos', filters={'Parent': doc.name}, fields=['etiqueta', 'observacion', 'bueno', 'malo'], order_by=\"name\") %}\n  {% for i in requi %}\n  {% set ns.sr = ns.sr + 1 %}\n  <tbody>\n    <tr style=\"padding: 1px!important;\" height=\"18px\">\n        \n        <td style=\"padding: 1px!important;\" width=\"50%\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:9px\">{{ns.sr}}.- {{i.etiqueta}}.</div>\n            \n        </td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 1px!important;\" width=\"2%\">\n             {%if i.bueno == 1 %} <div style = \"text-align: center;font-size:9px\"><span><strong> \u2713 </strong></span></div> {% endif %}\n        </td>\n        <td style=\"padding: 1px!important;\" width=\"2%\">\n             {%if i.malo == 1 %} <div style = \"text-align: center;font-size:9px;\"> <span><strong> \u2713 </strong></span> </div> {% endif %} \n        </td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: left; padding: 1px!important;\" width=\"46%\">\n             {%if i.observacion %} <div style = \"font-size:70%!important;\"><span>  {{i.observacion.upper()}}</span> </div> {% endif %}\n        </td>        \n    </tr>\n  </tbody>    \n{% endfor %}\n</table>\n\n<br>\n\n\n<div style = \"text-align: center;color:black;font-size:11px; \"><strong> COLOCACI\u00d3N DE CALCAS</strong></div>\n<table  border=\"1\" style=\"width:100%; height:100px\">\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td>\n                \n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n<table border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" >\n    <tr style=\"text-align: center;\">\n        <td width=\"30%\" style=\"font-size:9px;border-style: none;border-top-style: hidden;border-right-style: hidden;border-left-style: hidden;\">\n            PERITO VERIFICADOR<br><br>\n        </td>\n        <td width=\"30%\" style=\"font-size:9px;border-style: none;border-top-style: hidden;border-right-style: hidden;border-left-style: hidden;\">\n            \n        </td>\n        <td width=\"30%\" style=\"font-size:9px;border-style: none;border-top-style: hidden;border-right-style: hidden;border-left-style: hidden;\">\n            PERMISIONARIO/ GESTOR/ CHOFER<br><br>\n        </td>        \n    </tr>\n    <tr style=\"text-align: center;\">\n        <td  width=\"30%\"  style=\"font-size:9px;padding: 0px!important;border-right-style: hidden;border-left-style: hidden;border-bottom-style: hidden;\">\n            NOMBRE\n        </td>\n        <td width=\"30%\" style=\"font-size:9px;padding: 0px!important;border-right-style: hidden;border-left-style: hidden;border-bottom-style: hidden;border-top-style: hidden;\">\n            \n        </td>\n        <td width=\"30%\"  style=\"font-size:9px;padding: 0px!important;border-right-style: hidden;border-left-style: hidden;border-bottom-style: hidden;\">\n            NOMBRE\n        </td>        \n    </tr>    \n</table>\n<div class=\"contenedorFooter\">\n  <img src=\"/files/logoInferiorMovilidad11.png\"> \n  <div class=\"centrado\"><small>Avenida Rey Nayar S/N. Esquina con Insurgentes, colonia Bur\u00f3cratas Federal, Tepic, Nayarit. Tel. (311) 2135712</small></div>\n</div>\n</div><!--div contenedor -->\n",
